title: Pete Davidson: Silencing Fans to Save His Feelings?
description:
As the youngest member to ever join SNL, Pete Davidson has been on the rise, starring in movies and putting out several comedy specials. But, has the fame gone to his head? In order to attend his comedy shows, Pete’s required fans to sign away their rights to give their opinions about his performance. Tune in as we break it all down!
